Goodreads Librarians Group
60267 members
last activity 30 minutes ago
A place where all Goodreads members can work together to improve the Goodreads book catalog. Non-librarians are welcome to join the group as well, to
A place where all Goodreads members can work together to improve the Goodreads book catalog. Non-librarians are welcome to join the group as well, to comment or request changes to book records.
For general comments on Goodreads and for requests for changes to the site, try the Feedback group or use the Contact Us link instead.
For tips on being a librarian, check out the
librarian manual
.
Goodreads Librarians are members who have applied for and received librarian status on Goodreads. They are able to edit and improve the Goodreads catalog, and have made it one of the better catalogs online.
Activities include combining editions, fixing book and author typos, adding book covers and discussing policies.
If you are having trouble finding the link to add a new thread, try this: https://www.goodreads.com/topic/new?context_id=220-goodreads-librarians-group&context_type=Group
